org.cef.callback

接口 CefMenuModel


  • public interface CefMenuModel
    Supports creation and modification of menus. See cef_menu_id_t for the command ids that have default implementations. All user-defined command ids should be between MENU_ID_USER_FIRST and MENU_ID_USER_LAST. The methods of this class can only be accessed on the browser process the UI thread. (支持创建和修改菜单。有关具有默认实现的命令ID，请参见cef_menu_id_t。所有用户定义的命令ID都应在MENU_ID_USER_FIRST和MENU_ID_USER_LAST之间。此类的方法只能在浏览器进程UI线程上访问。)
